parameters: Glory to Heaven, glory to Him,
who alone is above all else!
He who shall guide us to the Holy Spirit!
He who shall wash our sins,
but especially Daphne's ugly contemptible unforgivable ones!
As filthy pagan evil has no place but in Oblivion!
You felons, evil-worshipping, perversion-supporters haven't won yet!!
You felons, nudity-totting, perversion-supporters haven't won yet!!
Watch in horror what we would have done to you,
and what you will suffer sooner or later in HELL!!
